_Pi’el_ Infinitive for regular shorushim:
The [[{{_pi’el_ infinitive}} form]] has the following conjugation pattern for [[regular shorushim]]:
| לְזַמֵּן <br><br> _lezamein_ <br><br><br> to invite |
For any regular shoresh, you can replace the letters ‎ז, ‎מ, and ן above with the letters of your shoresh to produce the proper conjugation.
